P_HTM[2004]="*taṃ, sāriputta, vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ diṭṭhiṃ appaṭinissajjitvā yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye.**Unless they give up that speech and that thought, and let go of that view, they will be cast down to hell.*";
